short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension for saving and managing Google Chrome tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Chrome extension for storing and manipulating whole tab sessions. Store all tabs from current window under named session with the ability to reopen it later in current/new session/window and incognito mode. Extension can be set to show all stored sessions as a new tab. All sessions can be exported to json file.
